itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaV52HYnriBec5fqaGBWoeLyc4yf2Q6m2RxgP7QFs7wFt?filename=sCcTd9O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCcTd9O.png&h=83e2c5a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40249cdd68f10b73a78c818645beb86c6576fbe6","tid":2493444,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">梵蒂岡國務卿主教樞機Parolin 捲入金融刑事調查醜聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2491354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2491354</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"}]}